&lt;li&gt;Data Protection and Security - The General Data Protection Regulation (GDPR) May 2018 and how it relates to your Clinical Coding role&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;The importance of maintaining confidentiality&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;The importance of information governance and the information governance toolkit&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&lt;/li&gt;
